    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte et individue trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/261">Chuonradus</persName> dei gratia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs> excellentissimus secundum voluntatem dei
                        salvatoris nostrique liberatoris. Quicquid confirmationis et proprietatis ad
                        ecclesiarum dei sanctorumque suorum exaltatione prebuerimus, id nobis ad
                        aeterne beatitudinis bravium et secularis vitae profectum esse profuturum
                        verissime credimus. Igitur omnium sanctae dei aecclesiae fidelium
                        nostrorumque presentium scilicet ac futurorum agnoscat universitas, qualiter
                        nos pro dei omnipotentis amore et pro anima amitae nostre <persName
                            ref="#people/1301" key="#Queen">Adheleidis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Queen">imperatricis</rs> augustae et ob remedium animae nostre
                        parentumque nostrorum, rogante domno <persName key="#Abbots"><name
                                ref="Maurus">Mauro</name></persName> venerabili <rs key="#Abbots"
                                    >abbate</rs>, suo <rs key="#Monasteries">cenobio</rs> ad honore <orgName
                                        key="#Rivers #Mountains #Villas #Curtes #Mansi #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Saltworks #Mills #Penalty #Cereals #Wine #Oil #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Castle #Ports #Other_administrative_unit #Assembly #Angaria #Tolls #Teloneum #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Immunity #Churches #Monasteries #Abbots #Monks #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius"
                                        ref="#juridical_persons/3619">sancti
                            Salvatoris</orgName> haud procul a menibus <placeName ref="#places/65"
                            >Ticinensis</placeName> urbis fundato per hoc nostrum <rs
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">regale preceptum</rs>, prout iuste et
                        legaliter valemus, confirmamus, quemadmodum ad antecessores meos preceptali
                        auctoritate confirmata sunt, omniaque eiusdem venerabili loco donata collata
                        et oblata sunt tam de largifluo dono memoratae amite nostre quam etiam
                        aliqua inscriptione cartarum aliorum hominum, cum <rs key="#Castle">castellis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Curtes">cortibus</rs> <rs key="#Royal_slave">servis</rs> 
                        <rs key="#Royal_slave">ancillis</rs> <rs key="#Royal_aldius">aldianibus</rs> et 
                        <rs key="#Royal_aldius">aldianis</rs> <rs key="#Churches">capellis</rs> oratoriis 
                        <rs key="#Villas">villis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">mansis</rs> <rs key="#Landed_possessions">campis</rs> 
                        <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs> <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs> <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pascuis</rs> 
                        <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs> <rs key="#Mountains">montibus</rs> vallibus planiciebus
                        <rs key="#Rivers">aquis aquarumque decursibus</rs> <rs key="#Fisheries">piscationibus</rs> 
                        <rs key="#Mills">molendinis</rs> terris cultis et
                        incultis <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">ripis</rs> 
                        <rs key="#Ports">portibus</rs>, verum etiam cum omnibus, de quibus venerabili
                        coenobium iuste investituram habet vel habuit ex ea die, qua prefata
                        serenissima imperatrix <rs key="#Monks">monachos</rs> ibi constituit. Confirmamus quidem et
                        firmissimam traditionem largimur eidem monasterio domini Salvatoris
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterium</rs> <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Monasteries"
                            >sancti Anastasii
                        </orgName> una cum curte <placeName
                            key="#Curtes 
                            #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/342">
                            <geogName
                                key="#Curtes 
                                #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#estates/134">Olonna</geogName></placeName>, <placeName
                                    key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                    >Montecelli</placeName>, <placeName
                                        key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                        >Aufenengo</placeName>,
                        <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Erbaria</placeName>, <placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Basiligutiam</placeName>, <placeName
                                    key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                    >Frisinariam</placeName>, <placeName
                                        key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                        >Pastorianum</placeName>, <placeName
                                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                            >Riuoceruinum</placeName>, <placeName
                                                key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                                >Tullianum</placeName>,
                        <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Puizolum</placeName>, <placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Centascum</placeName>, <placeName
                                    key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                    >Noue</placeName>, <placeName
                                        key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                        >Urba</placeName>, <placeName
                                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                            >Marinco</placeName>, <placeName
                                                key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                                >Corianum</placeName> cum omnibus pertitentiis
                        suis, <rs key="#Castle">castellum</rs> da Bosco, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Felegariolo</placeName>, terram de <persName key="#Landed_possessions">
                                <name ref="Petrus Albesanus">Petro Albesano</name></persName>, terram quam
                        tenuit <persName
                            key="#Landed_possessions"><name ref="Liudualdus"
                                >Liutaldus</name></persName> cum <rs key="#Mansi">manso</rs> de 
                        <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">
                            <geogName key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">Pelenzona</geogName></placeName>, 
                        <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Armentaria</placeName>, <placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Blundi</placeName>, <placeName
                                    key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                    >Gagio</placeName>,
                        <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Lagussianum</placeName>, <placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Cassina</placeName>, <placeName
                                    key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                    >Cuguzuda</placeName>, <placeName
                                        key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                        >Garlascum</placeName> cum <rs key="#Other_administrative_unit"
                                            >districtum</rs> in circuitu duo
                        miliarium una cum <rs key="#Forests">silva</rs> de Carbonaria, de quantum iam dictum monasterium per
                        preceptum tenere videtur, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Cauconate</placeName>, viridiarium prope Palatinam portam et
                        sancti Iohannis situm cum omnibus pertinentiis et adiacentiis suis tam infra
                        civitatem Ticinensem quam extra, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Garfiniana</placeName>, <placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Uicolongo</placeName>, <placeName
                                    key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                    >Bissione</placeName>, cellam
                        <orgName key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">sancti Nazarii</orgName>, 
                        <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Uirgemini</placeName>, <placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Mauratica</placeName>, <placeName
                                    key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                    >Melaria</placeName>. Insuper monasterium 
                        <orgName key="#Saltworks #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/1460">sancte
                        dei genitricis Mariae</orgName> in loco <placeName key="#places/4179">Ponposa</placeName> constructum, eum quibus ad eum
                        pertinere vi videtur, vel etiam omnes <rs key="#Saltworks">salinas</rs>, quam in 
                        <placeName key="#Saltworks" ref="#places/485">Comaclo</placeName> ab supra
                        scripto monasterio domini Salvatoris pertinere decernitur, seu in aliis
                        omnibus locis, que iam dicto coenobio sancti Salvatoris pertinere
                        cernuntur, illo in proprium corroboramus. Precipientes itaque iubemus, ut
                        <rs key="#Immunity #Exemption">nullus episcopus dux marchio comes vicecomes castaldius nullaque regni
                        nostri magna parvaque persona de rebus mobilibus sive immobilibus sive de
                        qualibet terra disvestire idem monasterium sine legali iuditio presumat</rs>.
                        Sancimus insuper et hac nostra regali auctoritate concedimus, ut, si
                        contigerit, quod sepe accidit, quatinus abbas prenominati monasterii huius
                        lucis habitaculum deserat, liceat monachos ex sinu eiusdem aecclesie quem
                        meliorem viderint eligere in patrem, omnium episcoporum vel omnium mortalium
                        contradictione remota, nec fas sit alicui monacho ex alio monasterio ad id
                        transitum facere sine voluntate monachorum inibi deo servientium in
                        perpetuum. Si quis autem huius nostrae promulgate auctoritatis et preceptis
                        violator extiterit sive predicte aecclesie sancti Salvatoris minorationem
                        facere aut in castellis villis vel aliquibuslibet locis eius aribergare,
                        <rs key="#Assembly">placitum</rs> sine eiusdem coenobii abbatis iussione ullatenus tenere aut aliquam
                        <rs key="#Angaria">angariam</rs> vel publicam functionem aut <rs key="#Teloneum">
                            theloneum</rs> extorquere vel tollere aut
                        monachos de aliqua re presumpserit molestare, sciat se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri
                        cocti libras mille</rs>, medietatem camere nostrae ac medietatem abbati eiusdem
                        monasterii qui pro tempore fuerit, et insuper, quod ei deterius est, cum
                        Iuda traditore domini salvatoris nostri, in cuius nomine iam dictum
                        monasterium constructum est, eternis deputetur incendiis. Ut autem verius
                        credatur hoc preceptum nostra auctoritate peractum, presentem paginam manu
                        propria, ut videtur infra, corroborante sigillo nostro iussimus insigniri.
                        Signum domni Chuonradi serenissimi regis. <persName key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Hugo">
                            Hugo</name></persName> <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> vice domni
                        <persName key="#Archchancellor #Archbishops" ref="#people/2127">Haribonis</persName> 
                        <rs key="#Archbishops">archiepiscopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor">archicancellarii</rs> 
                        recognovit. (SI. D.) Datum anno
                        dominicae incarnationis mileximo XXVI, indicione VIIII, regni vero domni
                        Chuonradi secundi regnantis II; actum <placeName ref="#places/43">Placentiae</placeName>; feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
